    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nSource code running result (python 3.12 and python 3.14):\n\n```python\nimport test_cython_annotation\n111 {'path': <class 'int'>, 'body': <class 'str'>}\n222 {'path': <class 'int'>, 'body': <class 'str'>}\n```\n\nCompile and run (python 3.12):\n\n```python\nimport test_cython_annotation\n111 {'path': <class 'int'>, 'body': <class 'str'>}\n222 {'path': <class 'int'>, 'body': <class 'str'>}\n```\n\nCompile and run (python 3.14):\n\n```python\nimport test_cython_annotation\n111 {'a': <class 'int'>, 'b': <class 'str'>}\n222 {'path': <class 'int'>, 'body': <class 'str'>}\n```\n\n### Code to reproduce the behaviour:\n\n**setup.py**\n\n```python\nimport sys\n\nfrom Cython.Build import cythonize\nfrom setuptools import setup, Extension\n\nif len(sys.argv) == 1:\n    sys.argv.extend([\"build_ext\", \"--inplace\", \"-j8\"])\n\nextensions = [\n    Extension(\n        \"test_cython_annotation\",\n        [\"test_cython_annotation.py\"],\n    )\n]\n\nsetup(\n    name=\"setup\",\n    ext_modules=cythonize(\n        module_list=extensions,\n        compiler_directives={'language_level': \"3\"},\n        build_dir=\"build/c\",\n        force=True\n    ),\n    zip_safe=False\n)\n\n\n```\n\n**test_cython_annotation.py**\n\n```python\nfrom typing import get_type_hints\nfrom functools import wraps\n\n\ndef deco(func):\n    @wraps(func)\n    def wrapper(a:int, b:str):\n        print(222, get_type_hints(func))\n        return func(a, b)\n\n    return wrapper\n\n\n@deco\ndef test(path: int, body: str):\n    pass\n\n\nprint(111, get_type_hints(test))\ntest(1, \"2\")\n```\n\n\n\n### Expected behaviour\n\nThe output result of python3.14 is the same as python3.12.\n\n### OS\n\nwindows\n\n### Python version\n\n3.12 &  3.14\n\n### Cython version\n\n3.2.4\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
